The '''State Administration of Work Safety''' ('''SAWS'''; {{zh|国家安全生产监督管理总局}}), reporting to the [[State Council of the People's Republic of China|State Council]], is the [[Ministry (government)|non-ministerial]] agency of the [[Government of the People's Republic of China]] responsible for the regulation of risks to [[occupational safety and health]] in [[China]].
